casebody.data:
Herman L. DOBSON, Jr.
v.
Theodis BECK. No. 363P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 12, 2005. Herman L. Dobson, Jr., Pro Se. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, Clark Everett, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 11th day of July 2005 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Pitt County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 12th day of July 2005."
